@page "/"

<PageTitle>Quants Agent - Home</PageTitle>

<div class="home-container">
    <h1>🤖 Quants Agent</h1>
    <h2>Multi-Agent Scenario Analysis Platform</h2>

    <div class="feature-description">
        <p>
            Run queries across multiple AI agents that take different perspectives and reason with each other — 
            building out the end-to-end view of potential outcomes for your analysis scenarios.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="method-cards">
        <a href="debate" class="method-card debate">
            <div class="method-icon">⚡</div>
            <h3>Debate</h3>
            <p>Fan-out parallel analysis. All agents analyze concurrently in swim lanes, then an orchestrator evaluates opinions across rounds until consensus is reached.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="compare" class="method-card compare">
            <div class="method-icon">🔀</div>
            <h3>Compare</h3>
            <p>Multi-model comparison. Models analyze in parallel swim lanes, while the orchestrator synthesizes differences in its own full-width row.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="turn" class="method-card turn">
            <div class="method-icon">🔄</div>
            <h3>Turn</h3>
            <p>Sequential turn-based analysis. Each agent is called one by one, building on previous insights in a vertical flow.</p>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="agent-cards">
        <div class="agent-card alpha">
            <div class="agent-avatar">📈</div>
            <h3>Alpha Quant</h3>
            <p>Identifies alpha opportunities, momentum signals, and favorable market conditions with data-driven reasoning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="agent-card pricing">
            <div class="agent-avatar">💰</div>
            <h3>Pricing Quant</h3>
            <p>Focuses on valuation models, pricing dynamics, and fair value assessments for instruments and strategies.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="agent-card risk">
            <div class="agent-avatar">🛡️</div>
            <h3>Risk Quant</h3>
            <p>Evaluates risk-adjusted returns, hedging strategies, and position sizing to balance opportunity with protection.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .home-container {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .home-container h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    .home-container h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #666;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-description {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .method-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .method-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        border-top: 4px solid #ddd;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .method-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .method-card.debate { border-top-color: #667eea; }
    .method-card.compare { border-top-color: #f59e0b; }
    .method-card.turn { border-top-color: #22c55e; }

    .method-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .method-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    .method-card p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .agent-cards {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .agent-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        border-left: 4px solid #ddd;
        text-align: left;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .agent-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .agent-card.alpha { border-left-color: #22c55e; }
    .agent-card.pricing { border-left-color: #3b82f6; }
    .agent-card.risk { border-left-color: #ef4444; }

    .agent-avatar {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .agent-card h3 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #1a1a2e;
    }

    .agent-card p {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #666;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .method-cards, .agent-cards {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
